title: Patch 6.6 Stuck At 33%
body: Hello, I was playing all night the night before the patch. I wake up this morning and get on league and seen there was a new patch. I updated and halfway through updating it says "Unspecified error, please check the logs for more information" I look up a fix for it. All of them were old and for older patches I tried some of  them none of them worked. I just uninstalled the whole client itself and tried reinstalling. Waited an hour and it still says the same error. This is only happening to me for patch 6.6 not sure whats happening but if anyone has a fix or could help me its very much appreciated <3 Thanks so much.

replies.body:
When you're getting stuck at 33%, it usually means there's some sort of connection error when the client is trying to download the new content.

I'd recommend taking a look at our [Patching Issues](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/202969434) and/or [Connection Troubleshooting](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) articles to see if those steps help. Lemme know if this works for you!
no one will help me so i am just replying to rioters, can you please check out my post I need help! thanks

If you're LoL update/download is stuck at 33% and/or your interface keeps scanning files, try this:

go to :RADS\projects\lol_patcher\releases\0.0.0.something
find this file: S_OK
go to other files in RADS\projects\
find 'releases' in them
put S_OK into every '0.0.sth' file that is missing it


TL;DR
Put S_OK file in all 0.0sth folders in the Releases folder.
